# App Rules

## app/app.py (Gradio)
- Copy vendor/MotionGPT/app.py to app/app.py, then adapt — do NOT rewrite from scratch
- FIRST LINE after imports: import matplotlib; matplotlib.use('Agg')
- Add gr.File output: "Download Activations (.npy)"
- Output filename: activations_{md5(prompt+timestamp)[:8]}.npy
- File format: float32 [T, 80] after Sigmoid — identical to P1 format
- Add activation heatmap as gr.Image (top-20 muscles, viridis, headless-safe PNG bytes)
- Expose api_name="predict" on inference function
- Load P1 visualization: sys.path.insert(0, config.app.p1_src_path) at startup
  - If import fails: log warning, skip visualization gracefully

## app/demo.py (CLI)
- Copy vendor/MotionGPT/demo.py, add:
  - --output-npy PATH: saves activations.npy
  - --show-activations: plots top-10 muscles via P1 visualization
- Default: identical to upstream demo.py

## Never call plt.show() — use fig.savefig(buf, format='png') with io.BytesIO()
